The Perfect Hard Boiled Egg

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:06.000
Hi, Welcome again to the flavor of my kitchen 

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:09.000
This is a quick recipe to show you 

00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:12.000
how I make the perfect hard boiled egg

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:15.000
when the yolk is still all yellow

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:18.000
and it does not get that grayish 

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:21.000
or greenish tint.  So in a small sauce pan or pot

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:24.000
I´m going to put water and turn the stove on high

