and immediately put two eggs

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:33.000
I will wait till the water boils  and let it boil

00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:36.000
for 3 minutes,  eggs and all

00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:42.000
Okay so the water

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:45.000
has started boiling  now i will let boil 

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:48.000
for exactly 3 minutes

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:03.000
Okay  it has been 3 min

00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:06.000
now im going to cover it and i will 

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:09.000
turn off the heat and let it rest

00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:12.000
for 10 uninterrupted minutes

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:15.000
do not open 

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:18.000
Okay  it has been

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:21.000
10 minutes  of resting

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:24.000
I´m going to take them out

